query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN lat IS NOT NULL AND lng IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_coords,
  SUM(CASE WHEN lat IS NULL OR lng IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_coords
FROM interpreters;
